Package: sds
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         libpaho-mqtt1.3,
         python3,
         python3-cffi
Description: SDS - Synchronized Data Structures for IoT
 A lightweight MQTT-based state synchronization library for IoT
 applications. Provides C library, Python bindings, and code generator.
 .
 Features:
  - Automatic state synchronization over MQTT
  - Owner/Device roles with config/state/status sections
  - Code generator for C and Python from .sds schema files
  - Arduino/ESP32 support via included library

Package: sds-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: sds (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: SDS - Development files
 Development headers for the SDS library.
 .
 This package contains the C headers needed to develop
 applications using the SDS library.
